## Running Examples

```bash
git clone https://github.com/nfraxlab/ai-infra.git
cd ai-infra
poetry install

# Chat
poetry run python -c "from ai_infra import LLM; print(LLM().chat('Hello!'))"

# Agent
poetry run python examples/agents/01_basic_tools.py

# See more examples
ls examples/
```

